[img=https://scontent-amt2-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/79783492_2709120449204175_7592547081680584704_o.jpg?_nc_cat=108&_nc_oc=AQnAdnjdaJbghwMVb3KczxGsfUxyAT2BYrOo9_bSI6HAWFzq6L3Ap8RY6YgjiqPgozyMm3Zki74i7QcZqS0o-RL4&_nc_ht=scontent-amt2-1.xx&oh=87f6d64286684e307f2220d9f501dca7&oe=5E6EF7B9]
Because I do have so many CD's and CDM's I might have many pieces twice, so these I can sell.

Sometimes I don't even know that I do have a CD / CDM for a long time, while I'm still searching for it ^+^
[img=https://scontent-amt2-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/79473686_2709122882537265_8863230550819733504_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&_nc_oc=AQlqTLKAOPflIfaI7uuIpG-YcAJ4LZPWao1qMku5fO_yvWLQHnhQl-EkdFeZpG6aI-n1qxk2w67nSGnzWQDwA1gc&_nc_ht=scontent-amt2-1.xx&oh=d907885caae6896c10cb24bbc1c8d25b&oe=5E6910B0]
Also I have many items packed in big boxes (400 pieces per box) and over 400 boxes and I still do not know what is in there...

So you might be looking for some CD/CD-MAXI  and I don't have it 'for sale' but I like to sell it though. 

Please ask me any CD/CD-MAXI you would like to have then I can take a look for you.

The chance is pretty big that I have what you want :)

[img=http://images2.fanpop.com/images/photos/7600000/Techno-techno-dream-trance-7696125-240-320.gif]
You may know that I am a real collector and all the CD's & CDM's are in a real good condition.
If not, I'll mention it.

You can be sure that even the jewelcase is factory new !
[img=https://media.giphy.com/media/QYdjRHqMNuxhxt0XQN/giphy.gif]

By buying from me I will make sure that I pack the CD with double care ! ^_^

Therefore I use special AirLite® Envelope's with Bubble Padding against any damaging in the postway.
Also addresses will not be written, but copied so all is clearly able to read.
My sender address is on the other side of the parcel printed the same way all with transparent tape over it to prevent from rain etc...  
[img=https://media.giphy.com/media/YRnB2gfdobYvcNCkYw/giphy.gif]
[img=https://scontent-amt2-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/80860229_2709125689203651_3058613766745751552_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&_nc_oc=AQnhD7EdlCtVkaPfcnbRmrSoNl3-wstAbIDmZ2R61fz2INPWwIf_bWfRndI3B3nOCWroEvpwkALSCpxkdSwMalaQ&_nc_ht=scontent-amt2-1.xx&oh=bc3713003003e7b8246ba00a571ce6f9&oe=5E783A91]

!!! But as everybody knows; Some postmen don't treat parcels always careful and so there is always a risk for broken jewelcases and/or not or late arriving...  !!!
[img=https://media.giphy.com/media/UTq46ta71u3p4yVOVS/giphy.gif]
If you want to have more safety for your CD's please ask for Registered Shipping.
This option has of-course another (higher) price.

I'll tell you the costs that will variate because of the weight and country.

[img=https://scontent-amt2-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p720x720/80301612_2709128399203380_6875464233908174848_o.jpg?_nc_cat=106&_nc_oc=AQlmrVXqwTA9_cT-iZDqaAAO9NQH4orTQzeAQ8DRccGzEqpoCEAq22cg9H3AFGhRuhTFcKs7565GZMFzT2NhRVDU&_nc_ht=scontent-amt2-1.xx&oh=92bf0443640543656bbfab1e00191dae&oe=5E6AF09A]

So all music friends all over the world, if you search for a CDM or CD ... Please ask me, or browse through my stock. 
[img=https://i.gifer.com/DrBy.gif]
Although there are over 2.000.000 items I own, I can't find the time to place all what I want to.

You can take a look on my "freewebs" site for eventually more titles.  http://www.freewebs.com/heelveelcds 
If this URL Link doesn't work please click on the original link above of this page ^_^

Also I started listing my CDM's in Excel and yet I'm counting 'till 54.821 (which are NOT listed at Discogs).

With a lot of CD's like mine there always might be there just what U R searching 4 for a Long Time ! ^_^
[img=https://i7.pngguru.com/preview/146/146/481/quality-clip-art-best-quality-high-quality-png.jpg]
I try to list as much as possible but it goes bit by bit. Simply can't find the time for it...
I don't have 25 hours a day ;-)

All questions are welcome and I'll try to answer them all as soon as possible :)
You even can send your "Wantlist" to me and I will take a look.
[img=https://media.giphy.com/media/xTiTnrAwCVnGTwWsOA/giphy.gif]
